data.revised_prompt: Design a simple and bold icon symbolizing the subject of 'Nutrition & Digestion.' The icon should feature stylized shapes like a stomach, fork, spoon, or simplified representations of fruits and vegetables. This could include a plate indicating the nutritional aspect, and the stomach indicating digestion. It's crucial that the design should remain minimalistic and be easy to recognize, even when scaled down. Set against a pure white background, the design should exclude any text or superfluous details.
